title: Can You See What I See.rar
description: Help an unfortunate shop owner save his collectibles shop in this original take on hidden object fun! Meet poor Clyde Curfuffle. He&#039;s suffered a fire, a flood, and a nasty fall that&#039;s left him in the hospital. This horrible string of bad luck means there&#039;s no one to run his fabulous shop! One of Clyde&#039;s favorite collectibles may sell for a lot of money, and he could really use a bit of good fortune, but you have to find out which one! Fill orders, find rare items, and solve a secret code to unravel a mystery that will save the day in level after level of stunning hidden object challenges. A unique treat for the entire family, Can You See What I See? is full of eye-popping fun!
